        <updateDate>2021-04-22T19:41:53Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Nuclear SLCM Ban Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the obligation or expenditure of Department of Defense or Department of Energy funds for FY2022, or any year thereafter, for the research and development, production, or deployment of the nuclear-armed sea-launched cruise missile and its associated nuclear warhead.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
